## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-org/your-repo.git
cd your-repo

##Build instructions.

###Windows:

Download and install Visual Studio 2022 (any edition).

Open the project file: ChaosGroove.sln build and run.

###Linux

make
chaos-groove-run.sh

###Linux/Wasm

Install emsdk

make -f makefile-web

or

make run -f makefile-web

